  #filter(period == "15 minutes") %>%

  #group_by(forecastid) %>%

  ungroup() %>%
  group_by(siteid, timestamp) %>%
  summarise_all(mean) %>%

    timestamp_key = floor_index(timestamp, unit = "days"),
    period = "daily"
  ) %>%
  select(-timestamp)
